name: Chess
body:
## Chess Engine/AI Project
This is a simple Chess engine and AI project. It is done solely for educational
purposes. You mustn't expect it to work in an efficient manner.

Currently the project is work in progress and shouldn't be downloaded for use. 

### How to access this repo:
```
$ cd Drigeolf/chess
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout gh-pages
```

If you're using the GitHub for Mac, simply sync your repository and you'll see the new branch.

### Authors and Contributors
Vedat Sinan Ural(@Drigeolf), Ali Sinan Saglam(@ASinanSaglam)

### Support or Contact
If you need to contact one of us, please use
the contact addresses included in the source code.
